# Walkthrough - Jin Hong M&E Website v4.0 Update

I have updated the `jin-hong-me-html-v2` website to align with the latest industrial and agentic standards.

## Key Accomplishments

### 1. Scroll-to-Top & Collision-Free UI
- **Scroll-to-Top Button**: Added a premium square button (45x45px, 8px radius) that fades in after scrolling 500px.
- **WhatsApp Integration**: Implemented a "collision-aware" logic where the WhatsApp button automatically shifts upward by 60px when the Scroll-to-Top button appears, ensuring a clean and accessible UI on all devices.

### 2. Animated Stats Ribbon
- Integrated an `IntersectionObserver` that triggers smooth number counting (e.g., 0 to 800+) when the stats section enters the user's viewport.
- Removed static numbers in favor of dynamic, tech-forward animations.

### 3. v4.0 Branding & Mandatory Credits
- **Footer Updates**: Corrected all footer credits to the mandatory format: `© 2026 JIN HONG M&E SDN BHD. All Rights Reserved. | Provided by Zeta Capital Sdn. Bhd.`
- **Consistency**: Synchronized headers and footers across all 10+ pages, including auxiliary pages like [privacy.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html-v2/privacy.html), [terms.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html-v2/terms.html), and [faq.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html-v2/faq.html).

### 4. Technical Refinements
- **Performance**: Optimized [global.css](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html-v2/css/global.css) and [main.js](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html-v2/js/main.js) to handle interactions without heavy dependencies.
- **Mandatory Logic**: Verified all internal links and ensured that the "Contact Us" CTA correctly defaults to WhatsApp.

